_:N79724599987a4ade9c9d69da03f7e30f <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Simon Claydon is the Director of Civil Service Pay, Policy and Pensions at the Cabinet Office.</p>\n\n<p>Simon was previously, from June 2021 to May 2023, the Director of People, Capability and Change at the Department for Levelling Up, Housing and Communities.</p>\n\n<p>In a 32 year Civil Service career, Simon has held a number of other senior HR and other leadership roles, including at HM Revenue and Customs, Cabinet Office and Department of Health and Social Care.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
